### ===== 【快速完整工作流测试】=====
### 按顺序执行这些请求来生成各种状态的数据

### ========== 生成 DRAFT 状态 ==========
### 创建文章1（保持DRAFT）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/content/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "文章1 - DRAFT状态",
  "content": "这篇文章只创建，不提交审核...",
  "creatorId": 2
}

###

### ========== 生成 PENDING 状态 ==========
### 创建文章2
POST http://localhost:8080/api/content/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "文章2 - PENDING状态",
  "content": "这篇文章创建后会提交审核...",
  "creatorId": 3
}

###

### 提交文章2审核（变成PENDING）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/content/2/submit-review?userId=3

###

### ========== 生成 APPROVED 状态 ==========
### 创建文章3
POST http://localhost:8080/api/content/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "文章3 - APPROVED状态",
  "content": "这篇文章会被审核通过...",
  "creatorId": 4
}

###

### 提交文章3审核
POST http://localhost:8080/api/content/3/submit-review?userId=4

###

### 审核通过文章3（变成APPROVED）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/content/audit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contentId": 3,
  "reviewerId": 5,
  "action": "APPROVED",
  "comment": "审核通过"
}

###

### ========== 生成 REJECTED 状态 ==========
### 创建文章4
POST http://localhost:8080/api/content/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "文章4 - REJECTED状态",
  "content": "这篇文章会被审核拒绝...",
  "creatorId": 2
}

###

### 提交文章4审核
POST http://localhost:8080/api/content/4/submit-review?userId=2

###

### 审核拒绝文章4（变成REJECTED）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/content/audit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contentId": 4,
  "reviewerId": 6,
  "action": "REJECTED",
  "comment": "内容不符合规范"
}

###

### ========== 生成 ONLINE 状态 ==========
### 创建文章5
POST http://localhost:8080/api/content/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "文章5 - ONLINE状态",
  "content": "这篇文章最后会被发布上线...",
  "creatorId": 3
}

###

### 提交文章5审核
POST http://localhost:8080/api/content/5/submit-review?userId=3

###

### 审核通过文章5
POST http://localhost:8080/api/content/audit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contentId": 5,
  "reviewerId": 5,
  "action": "APPROVED",
  "comment": "通过审核"
}

###

### 发布文章5（变成ONLINE）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/content/5/publish?userId=3

###

### ========== 生成 OFFLINE 状态 ==========
### 创建文章6
POST http://localhost:8080/api/content/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "文章6 - OFFLINE状态",
  "content": "这篇文章会被发布后再下线...",
  "creatorId": 4
}

###

### 提交文章6审核
POST http://localhost:8080/api/content/6/submit-review?userId=4

###

### 审核通过文章6
POST http://localhost:8080/api/content/audit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contentId": 6,
  "reviewerId": 6,
  "action": "APPROVED",
  "comment": "通过"
}

###

### 发布文章6
POST http://localhost:8080/api/content/6/publish?userId=4

###

### 下线文章6（变成OFFLINE）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/content/6/offline?userId=4

###

### ========== 查询验证 ==========
### 查看所有内容
GET http://localhost:8080/api/content/list?page=1&pageSize=20

###

### 查看各状态统计
### DRAFT
GET http://localhost:8080/api/content/list?status=DRAFT

###

### PENDING
GET http://localhost:8080/api/content/list?status=PENDING

###

### APPROVED
GET http://localhost:8080/api/content/list?status=APPROVED

###

### REJECTED
GET http://localhost:8080/api/content/list?status=REJECTED

###

### ONLINE
GET http://localhost:8080/api/content/list?status=ONLINE

###

### OFFLINE
GET http://localhost:8080/api/content/list?status=OFFLINE

